# Kairos Ontology Toolkit — AI Provider Configuration
#
# This file configures the LLM backend used by `kairos-ontology analyse-sources`.
# Copy to `.env` in your hub root and fill in your chosen provider.
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTION 1: GitHub Models (default, free for open-source)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTION 2: Azure AI Foundry (legacy OpenAI-compatible endpoint)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPORTANT: Use the OpenAI-compatible endpoint format (with /openai/v1 suffix).
# This works with gpt-5.4-mini and other chat models without needing api-version.
#
# Format: https://<resource>.services.ai.azure.com/openai/v1
# Do NOT use: https://<resource>.services.ai.azure.com/api/projects/<project>
#   (that format requires the Foundry SDK — see OPTION 3)
#
# KAIROS_AI_PROVIDER=azure
# AZURE_AI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.services.ai.azure.com/openai/v1
# AZURE_AI_KEY=your_api_key_here

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTION 3: Microsoft Foundry (recommended for enterprise)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Uses the azure-ai-projects SDK with the Foundry project endpoint.
# Install: pip install kairos-ontology-toolkit[foundry]
#
# Format: https://<resource>.services.ai.azure.com/api/projects/<project>
#
# KAIROS_AI_PROVIDER=foundry
# AZURE_FOUNDRY_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.services.ai.azure.com/api/projects/your-project
# AZURE_FOUNDRY_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
#
# For Entra ID auth (recommended, no key needed):
# Just set AZURE_FOUNDRY_ENDPOINT — DefaultAzureCredential handles auth.
# Requires the "Foundry User" (or higher) RBAC role on the Foundry resource.

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Model override (optional — default: gpt-5.4-mini)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# KAIROS_AI_MODEL=gpt-5.4-mini
